Zeneca                                 1.99
Du Pont                                1.96
Bayer                                  1.94
Rhone-Poulenc                          1.93
Monsanto                               1.65
Dow Elanco                             1.58
Hoechst                                1.39
BASF                                   1.19
American Cyanamid                      1.00
Sandoz                                 0.88
Schering                               0.82
 -------------------------------------------------------
Source: Wood Mackenzie
