handbags and, in time, this will offer considerable scope for broadening the
product range.'
These most recent investments came together when Time Products was awarded
the North American agency for Audemars Piguet, having distributed its
watches in the UK for a number of years. A luxury watch showroom is now
being developed at the premises of Judith Leiber in New York.
