Zeneca to new-ICI.
Zeneca ex-rights fell from a first price of 682p to 664p, little more than a
10 per cent premium to the rights price, where they yield 5.2 per cent. That
compares, institutions said, with a yield for Glaxo of 3.5 per cent or
Wellcome of 2.5 per cent.
