</XX>
<IN>P9199 General Government, NEC.
    P9611 Administration of General Economic Programs.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
</XX>
<TP>ECON  Industrial production.
    ECON  Inflation.
    GOVT  Government News.
</TP>
